<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jul1917"><font color="red">8 July 1917</font>, <cite>Letters II</cite> (JJ to James B. Pinker): I am engaged in writing a book (<cite>Ulysses</cite>) and I want to have <cite>Exiles</cite> published this autumn so that I may be able to continue to write it. I foresee for it more difficulties &hellip; a grave and dangerous illness extending over five months</div>
